            <div class="project-card-component">
                <div class="project-card-article">
                    <h1>OSHOP</h1>
                    <h3>
                        The project involves building an online grocery website. The website will is developed with Angular frontend framework for the client-side, web API powered by Node.js, and data is stored and managed by using MongoDB.
                    </h3>
                    <p>The integration of Angular, Node.js, and MongoDB provides a powerful stack for building a scalable and responsive online grocery website. This technology combination enables me to create a modern and intuitive user interface, develop a robust backend API for managing business processes, and efficiently store and retrieve data by using MongoDB. With these tools, I'm able to deliver a online shopping experience for customers, allowing them to browse and purchase groceries with ease.</p>
                </div>
                
