            </div>
            <div class="project-card-component">
                <div class="project-card-article">
                    <h1>POS RESTAURANT</h1>
                    <h3>
                        The project develops a "Point of Sale" (POS) application specifically designed for restaurant use. The application was built using the C# programming language, leveraging the .NET framework with the Model-View-Controller (MVC) architectural pattern. The data is stored and managed by using a SQL database, with the addition of trigger functions.
                    </h3>
                    <p>This a group project from the course Advanced Database, these technology help me to create a user-friendly interface, implement business logic, manage data effectively for applications commonly used in restaurant environments in the future.</p>
                </div>
                
            </div>
            
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="currency bd-container" id="currency">
        <div class="project-card projects-bd-flex">
            <div class="project-card-img">
