            </div>
            <div class="project-card-component">
                <div class="project-card-article">
                    <h1>TY GIA VANG (Gold Price & Currency Rates)</h1>
                    <h3>
                        This mobile app provides information about gold prices and currency rates. The app is built using the React Native framework, with the backend powered by Node.js for the web API, and MongoDB serving as the database.
                    </h3>
                    <p>The app will likely include features such as real-time updates, historical data, and possibly a tool for exchanging different currencies. With this project, I combine different technologies to deliver a comprehensive mobile app that caters to users interested in tracking gold prices and currency rates. By leveraging React Native, Node.js, and MongoDB, it enables me to build a responsive, scalable, and efficient application.</p>
                </div>
                
            </div>
            
        </div>
    </section>
